<h4 id="toc18"><span>Fanart</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://psychologist-frog.tumblr.com/">Dr. Frog</a> has given us a creeptastic image of a good horror article, <a href="/scp-1730">SCP-1730</a>. You can see the leech boy in his gross glory <a href="http://psychologist-frog.tumblr.com/post/139787534076/and-heres-the-leech-boy-scp-1730-written-by">here</a>!</li>
<li>Ever wish the SCP Foundation had a movie or TV adaptation? You can keep imagining how cool that would look with <a href="http://sexycontainmentprocedures.tumblr.com/post/139697000322/coming-soon-to-a-theater-near-you-the-series">these posters</a>, made by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5888483); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5888483&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869488" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5888483)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5888483); return false;">Cyantreuse</a></span>! You can check out her gallery of work <a href="http://sexycontainmentprocedures.tumblr.com/gallery">here</a>! (Blog NSFW).</li>
<li>And speaking of cool posters, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drkens" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304092); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=304092&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869488" alt="DrKens" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=304092)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drkens" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304092); return false;">DrKens</a></span> created some cool movie poster mockups for various contest teams! <a href="http://camerapits.tumblr.com/post/140275303417/camerapits-do-you-hunt-in-words-as-before">This one</a> is MTF Tau-5 (&quot;Samsara&quot;), created by the Apotheosis team. Check out his tumblr <a href="http://camerapits.tumblr.com/">here</a>!</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=3354281">芥绿</a> made a wonderful comic for a <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/a-restless-wanderer-on-the-earth">cool WL tale</a>! You can check it out <a href="http://www.pixiv.net/member_illust.php?mode=medium&amp;illust_id=55234992">here</a> and get emotional :')</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<p>Thanks for tuning in again, guys! I apologize for delivering late this month and last month. I will figure out a way to repay for my sins, but in the mean time, enjoy!</p>
